00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:05,764 --> 00:01:08,196
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,324 --> 00:01:11,236
=Episode 18=

3
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,000
Again.

4
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:25,719
Again!

5
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:34,799
Again!

6
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,040
Your Majesty.

7
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,680
His Majesty has things to do later.

8
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:53,760
I shall drink with you now.
Thank you for coming.

9
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,879
I once heard from His Majesty

10
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:05,719
that you're an excellent woman.

11
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:08,599
Indeed, seeing is believing.

12
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,759
When it comes to drinking,

13
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,199
I like the way your people drink.
They drink heartily.

14
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:15,439
I heard from His Majesty

15
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:18,520
that you have great military abilities.

16
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:21,759
I guess your martial arts must be good.

17
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,560
Of course.

18
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:27,280
Women of Central Plains also possess
loyal hearts to defend our homeland.

19
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,639
Sit still.

20
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:31,819
Sit still.

21
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,000
Impressive.

22
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:10,400
- Impressive.
- Impressive.

23
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,280
Fantastic!

24
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:12,240
Impressive!

25
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,360
Impressive.

26
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:50,319
(Xu Yu can both
wield a sword and drink.)

27
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,600
(Even her behavior is no different
from before.)

28
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:55,959
(In contrast, Xiao Jinyun
has reverted to his previous demeanor.)

29
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:58,680
(Could it be that the incident
at the altar)

30
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,000
(helped switch their bodies back?)

31
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:05,079
You mean
the Emperor of Chen values scholarship

32
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,199
and knows nothing of martial arts?

33
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,519
Yet the Empress
is the daughter of a general

34
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,279
and knows martial skills?

35
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:13,720
Exactly.

36
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,879
(Not just sword dancing,)

37
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,040
(even the way she drank is identical.)

38
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,680
(Can there truly be two people
whose behaviors are so similar?)

39
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,759
(Or perhaps...)

40
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,079
Your Majesty.

41
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,560
Queen Dada requests a meeting.

42
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,800
Huna?

43
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:58,279
Let her in.

44
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,319
Yes.

45
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,199
Greetings, Your Majesty.

46
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,720
I'm here

47
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:22,040
to thank Your Majesty for exempting Dada
from tribute for three years.

48
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,560
Since we are allies,

49
00:06:24,519 --> 00:06:26,800
no need to thank me for that.

50
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,560
Indeed.

51
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,639
After all, when you were in Dada,

52
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,040
Your Majesty guaranteed

53
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,600
that if Dada is in a crisis,

54
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,160
no matter when,

55
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,759
you will come to help.

56
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:44,920
Of course.

57
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,360
Since that is the case,

58
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:48,800
I have another request.

59
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,240
Speak plainly.

60
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,279
I wish to see the Majesty again

61
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,600
that I encountered in the desert.

62
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,879
You invited me to watch the flowers.

63
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,000
Yet you are not here.

64
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,959
Queen of Dada?

65
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,439
What brings you here?

66
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:26,120
I asked His Majesty to arrange this.

67
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,399
Why?

68
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:32,519
I wasn't sure
if I should invite His Majesty,

69
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,160
or Her Majesty,
whom I met in the desert.

70
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,000
How did you know?

71
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,560
I consulted our shaman.

72
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,800
Soul Silk is a treasure of Dada.

73
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,920
And the witchcraft is unique to Dada.

74
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:50,519
Coupled with your martial arts
and drinking habits,

75
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:53,759
I deduced that your bodies were swapped.

76
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,439
Since you already know...

77
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:00,879
Don't worry.

78
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:04,240
The people of Dada
will always be your friends.

79
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,800
Wonderful!

80
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,279
You're not even angry?

81
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,360
What's so great about Huna?

82
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:29,959
His Majesty is actually enchanted
by that seductress!

83
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,200
(They are hugging)

84
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,440
(and smiling so sweetly.)

85
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,840
It's a load off my mind.

86
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,399
From now on,
we can speak freely just like before.

87
00:08:44,919 --> 00:08:45,419
Okay.

88
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,759
That's it.

89
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:05,600
You're doing much better than I did.

90
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,519
Such a large garden.

91
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,480
If it's filled with flowers in spring,

92
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:12,360
it must be like a paradise on earth.

93
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,759
These plants are deliberately planted

94
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,960
and can't compare to those
in Moon Valley.

95
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,720
Does it hurt?

96
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,440
When I first learned,
I got pricked many times a day.

97
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,679
It's fine.

98
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,299
Giddy up!

99
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:10,779
Giddy up!

100
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,340
Giddy up!

101
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,759
May our friendship last forever.

102
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,759
(Your Majesty.)

103
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:51,600
(You've never been this thoughtful
towards me.)

104
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,240
One, two, three, go.

105
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:57,120
One, two, three, go.

106
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,460
Well done.

107
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:02,820
Don't move.

108
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,679
Don't move.

109
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,200
Good.

110
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,399
Good.

111
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:08,480
Go on.

112
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,000
One, two, three.

113
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,879
What are you doing here?

114
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:22,960
And what about you?

115
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,799
Must I explain to you?

116
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:33,639
You look suspicious.

117
00:11:34,879 --> 00:11:36,080
You must be up to no good.

118
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,120
(Xu Yu.)

119
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,919
(You've been pretending for so long.)

120
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,120
(Still not satisfied?)

121
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:43,919
(Drop the act!)

122
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,919
Consort Zhao.

123
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:55,159
Consort Zhao, what brings you here?

124
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,879
I wish

125
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:08,399
to get close to Your Majesty's friends.

126
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,360
You also know martial arts?

127
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:14,740
Come on.

128
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,360
Consort Zhao,

129
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:20,279
are you alright?

130
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,519
Consort Zhao,

131
00:12:24,519 --> 00:12:25,840
won't you stay longer?

132
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:30,399
Try it. This is the best liquor
in our palace.

133
00:12:54,759 --> 00:12:55,259
How is it?

134
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:58,039
Chen's wine is good

135
00:12:58,679 --> 00:12:59,759
but somewhat mild.

136
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:03,240
The strong liquor is spicy,

137
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,679
intense, and direct,

138
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,519
while the mild one

139
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,679
is refined

140
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,840
and not bland,

141
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,159
with a long, clean finish

142
00:13:11,279 --> 00:13:12,360
and balanced flavors.

143
00:13:12,759 --> 00:13:13,600
Each has its merits.

144
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:15,759
It's just a matter of personal taste.

145
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:18,679
But I think you suit the strong liquor.

146
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:20,240
You suit the boundless grasslands,

147
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,639
instead of being trapped
by the palace walls.

148
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,360
You shouldn't waste energy

149
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,159
on being envied.

150
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,200
As the Empress,

151
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,879
I willingly wish to assist His Majesty.

152
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:32,000
As a wife,

153
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,200
I love my husband wholeheartedly.

154
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,360
After parting,

155
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,039
I dreamed of coming to Chen.

156
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:40,559
I'm grateful for helping me
reclaim the throne.

157
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:42,080
Unexpectedly, he is the Emperor.

158
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:44,440
These past few days, I've sensed it.

159
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,080
He's been secretly watching us.

160
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,200
Truly petty.

161
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:50,720
Listen, he's not really like that.

162
00:13:50,799 --> 00:13:52,720
He's just naturally cautious.

163
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,039
He doesn't yet trust or know you well.

164
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:57,799
Xu Yu is right.

165
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:01,240
I truly don't know you well.

166
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:05,679
But can you give me a chance?

167
00:14:08,399 --> 00:14:09,240
I believe

168
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:11,200
drinking capacity isn't key,

169
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:14,679
but one should know how to accept,

170
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,159
wake up to reality, and reflect.

171
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,120
Coincidentally, I know all these.

172
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,159
Come on, drink.

173
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:27,679
So this is Your Majesty's intention.

174
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:31,080
But persistence and resolve
are also crucial.

175
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,600
Drink up.

176
00:14:44,399 --> 00:14:44,899
Excellent.

177
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:46,039
What a coincidence.

178
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:46,960
Let's eat together.

179
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:47,759
Come on.

180
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,120
Another cup.

181
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:02,519
(Why are they competing like this?)

182
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:12,240
Why must you drink?

183
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,720
I can drink.

184
00:15:17,639 --> 00:15:18,399
Over here.

185
00:15:25,679 --> 00:15:27,240
I'll get you some water.

186
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,559
Every time you're drunk, you kiss me.

187
00:15:49,919 --> 00:15:51,039
Xu Yu,

188
00:15:52,279 --> 00:15:54,960
if I could always kiss you,

189
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,159
I would rather

190
00:15:58,039 --> 00:16:00,080
stay drunk forever,
and never sober up again.

191
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,039
Xiao Jinyun,

192
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:05,759
you are actually making me shy.

193
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:10,799
I can give up anything for you.

194
00:16:11,399 --> 00:16:12,480
I never regret it.

195
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:16,679
All I hope is to stay with you.

196
00:16:19,139 --> 00:16:19,639
Alright.

197
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:20,279
Enough.

198
00:16:20,279 --> 00:16:21,240
Stop talking.

199
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,320
Xu Yu,

200
00:16:25,559 --> 00:16:27,320
I said every word

201
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,600
from the bottom of my heart.

202
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:32,039
I'm serious.

203
00:16:35,552 --> 00:16:41,079
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

204
00:16:41,184 --> 00:16:43,264
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

205
00:16:43,264 --> 00:16:47,584
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

206
00:16:47,584 --> 00:16:52,672
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

207
00:16:52,672 --> 00:16:54,720
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

208
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:58,872
♪This life is but a solitary boat♪

209
00:16:58,872 --> 00:17:05,184
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

210
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:15,799
Your Highness.

211
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,839
It's a letter from Dada.

212
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,599
Water and fire suppress each other.

213
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:32,640
Yin and Yang merge.

214
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,119
Souls return to their places.

215
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,359
(My guess was right.)

216
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,359
(Xu Yu has returned.)

217
00:17:53,759 --> 00:17:56,319
(And Xiao Jinyun wishes for peace.)

218
00:17:57,079 --> 00:17:59,680
(So I can't let him get his wish.)

219
00:18:16,324 --> 00:18:21,508
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

220
00:18:22,244 --> 00:18:26,807
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

221
00:18:28,132 --> 00:18:33,547
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

222
00:18:34,116 --> 00:18:38,660
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

223
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:44,564
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

224
00:18:44,932 --> 00:18:50,609
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

225
00:18:50,948 --> 00:18:52,964
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

226
00:18:53,156 --> 00:18:56,900
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

227
00:18:57,476 --> 00:19:02,148
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

228
00:19:02,692 --> 00:19:04,452
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

229
00:19:04,772 --> 00:19:08,388
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

230
00:19:08,635 --> 00:19:14,162
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

